item.title: Trump sends Tom Homan to Minnesota to manage ICE after Alex Pretti killing
item.description: The killing of ICU nurse Alex Pretti by federal agents in Minneapolis, like the fatal shooting of Renee Good by an ICE officer, was caught on video.

item.title: Treasury cancels Booz Allen contracts after employee leaked Trump tax records; stock falls
item.description: Booze Allen employee Charles Edward Littlejohn also had leaked tax records of Amazon's Jeff Bezos and Tesla chief Elon Musk to a news outlet.

item.title: Videos of Alex Pretti shooting by federal agents in Minneapolis contradict Trump official claims
item.description: Footage from at least one of the videos appears to show a federal officer disarming the victim before shots are fired.

item.title: Shutdown odds grow as Senate Republicans won't remove DHS funding after Pretti killing
item.description: Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer of New York says he'll vote against DHS funding after federal agents fatally shot Alex Pretti in Minneapolis.
